title: Joe Rogan Experience Review 176
description:
We were supposed to get to the Sean Carroll one too but we ran over the time we had. It's very interesting though so make sure to check that podcast out if you're into physics.

This episode we covered:

1350 Nick Bostrom the Swedish philosopher that annoys Joe with his complicated simulation theory

1351 Dan Aykroyd is a legendary comedian and a bit of a UFO conspiracy theorist.

Enjoy my review folks!
